history.content: Should be fine. I took 61C my first semester junior year and EE16A my second semester junior year and had no trouble getting in since I was declared. Although being declared doesn’t matter for those two classes anyway since they are big. I’m guessing it will be easier to get into 16B than 16A since less people are required to take it.

Im currently a rising sophomore and am an intended CS major. I am planning to only take CS61B next fall and CS70 in the spring because I am worried about declaring/ do not think doing EE16B and CS61B together and CS70 and CS61C together would be a good idea for me. Will I have trouble getting into CS61C and EE16B as a junior if I am able to declare CS?
history.subject: Holding off EE16B and CS61C
